{"abstract":[{"text":"These ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tokens"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" are defined for components and refer to semantic tokens or raw tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"They can be seen as a kind of bridge between components and in the end primitive values of the design kit.","type":"text"}],"topicSections":[{"anchor":"Group","title":"Group","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/BadgeComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/BulletListComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ButtonComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/CheckboxComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ChipComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ControlItemComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/DividerComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ExpandLinkComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/IconComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/LinkComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/PinCodeInputComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/QuantityInputComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/RadioButtonComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/SelectInputComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/SkeletonComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/SwitchComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/TagComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/InputTagComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/TextAreaComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/TextInputComponentTokens"]},{"anchor":"Protocols","generated":true,"title":"Protocols","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ButtonMonoComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/LinkMonoComponentTokens"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","level":2},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":["🧬 Core version: 1.8.0"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Thus if a component need to change for example its "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"background color"}]},{"type":"text","text":", and if a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"component token","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" is used for it, then only the value of this "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"token"}]},{"type":"text","text":" should be changed without any modification on the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component"}]},{"type":"text","text":" definition."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components"}]},{"type":"text","text":" use "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"component tokens","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" exposed through the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme"}]},{"type":"text","text":" thanks to token providers to get their style values."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components tokens are defined and gathered inside "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift protocol","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" so as to be exposed then through implementation of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" thanks to dedicated tokens providers."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because we choose to split responsabilities and objects into their own modules, we faced troubles to make possible for children themes or providers to override properties declared in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"protocols","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and defined in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"extensions"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"That is the reason why tokens are exposed as "},{"code":"@objc open","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to be available and overridable anywhere."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Example with ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ButtonComponentTokens","isActive":true},{"text":":","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Declare some component tokens for buttons with properties they must apply","public protocol ButtonComponentTokens {","    var sizeMaxHeightIconOnly: SizeSemanticToken { get }","    var buttonBorderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { get }","    var buttonBorderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { get }","    var colorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { get }","    var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { get }","}","","\/\/ There is an existing provider for such tokens","open class OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider { }","","\/\/ Define the components tokens exposed through the theme thanks to provider","extension OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider: ButtonComponentTokens {","","    \/\/ Raw tokens can be used","","    @objc open var sizeMaxHeightIconOnly: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._600 }","    ","    \/\/ And also semantic tokens","","    @objc open var buttonBorderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.widthThicker }","    @objc open var buttonBorderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { borders.radiusMedium }","    @objc open var colorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.repositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","    @objc open var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineSpacious }","}","","\/\/ This provider is then exposed through OUDSTheme as an AllButtonComponentTokensProvider"]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"How to use component tokens","anchor":"How-to-use-component-tokens"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In fact, the component tokens are declared and gathered in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Swift protocol","type":"text"}]},{"text":" so as to force any theme to implement them, and also to allow any theme to expose such properties whathever the implementation of the theme is, across providers.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Because ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component tokens"}]},{"text":" have for values ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"raw tokens","type":"text"}]},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"semantic tokens","type":"text"}]},{"text":", and in the end for values primitive types, and all these tokens are declared with ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"type aliases","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" refering all together, you can handle a ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component token"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" directly in your view because the final value will be used.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Thus, get the theme and call the needed property with some helpers.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct SomeView: View {","","    @Environment(\\.theme) private var theme \/\/ Supposed you used in your root view the `OUDSThemeableView` to register the theme","    @Environment(\\.colorScheme) private var colorScheme","","    var body: some View {","        Button {","            \/\/ Some action","        } label: {","            Text(\"Some label\")","                .cornerRadius(theme.button.buttonBorderRadius)","        }","        .padding(.leading, theme.button.spacePaddingInlineChevronStart)","        .padding(.trailing, theme.button.spacePaddingInlineChevronEnd)","        .background(theme.button.colorBgStrongEnabledMono)","        .overlay(","            RoundedRectangle(cornerRadius: theme.button.buttonBorderRadius)","                .stroke(Color.blue, lineWidth: theme.button.buttonBorderWidthDefault)","        )","    }","\/*","    - The theme provides border semantic tokens \"buttonBorderRadius\" and \"buttonBorderWidthDefault\"","    - The theme provides a color semantic token \"colorBgStrongEnabledMono\"","    - The theme provides spaces semantic token \"spacePaddingInlineChevronStart\" and \"spacePaddingInlineChevronEnd\"","*\/","}","","\/\/ Do not forget in your app to use the `OUDSThemeableView` for your theme, e.g. `OrangeTheme`","@main","struct DesignToolbox: App {","","    var body: some Scene {","        WindowGroup {","            OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","                ...","            }","        }","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The components tokens are wrapped in tokens provider acessible through the themes:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"table","rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Components tokens provider","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Target component"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"badge","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For badges like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSBadge","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"button"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For buttons like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSButton","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"bulletList","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For list of elements with bullets"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"checkbox"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For checkboxes like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckbox"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"type":"text","text":" and their indeterminate variants"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"chip"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For chips like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSuggestionChip"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSFilterChip"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"controlItem"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Shared and sued for switch, checkbox and radio items layouts","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"divider","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For dividers like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSHorizontalDivider"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSVerticalDivider"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"icon","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For components containing icons like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTag"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"link"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For links like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSLink"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"pinCodeInput","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"quantityInput"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"radioButton","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For radio components like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadio"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadioItem"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"selectInput","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"skeleton"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"switch"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For switch components like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSwitch"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSwitchItem"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"tag","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For tag components like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTag"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"inputTag"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For input tag components like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSInputTag","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"textArea"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For text area components like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTextArea","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"textInput","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For text field input components like "},{"code":"OUDSTextInput","type":"codeVoice"}]}]]],"header":"row"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[[]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/docu